    "We next discuss the key components needed to provide instructibility to the LMM.",
    "We begin by detailing the framework incorporating communication context, prompting, and an online LMM with wireless environment feedback, contributing to establishing an instructible system.",
    "Subsequently, we explore how to gain crucial qualities, such as logical and mathematical reasoning, that are pivotal for constructing self-evolving and dynamically adaptable systems, thus achieving instructibility.1) Communication context: Causal representations that are used to represent the physical symbols, similar to tokens in NLP-based LLMs, form the communication context for an LMM.",
